{"tid":1464054,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"荷蘭籍女士：理解示威者在機場的行動","createTime":"2019-08-13T14:20:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T15:36:15.000Z","uid":60545,"like":284,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":40,"replies":[{"pid":"b1e81ec933b5fecc2ad8a6b0d53b33a1dd3b0ddc","tid":1464054,"uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:20:08.000Z","msg":"【學苑即時】居港逾廿年的荷蘭籍女士Irma表示理解示威者在機場的行動，她贊同集會有效，令其在歐洲的親友也因此詢問香港的現況。她續指堵塞離境大堂雖非合適的地方，但仍然支持示威者爭取民主的決心。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/393883453958717/posts/3468724909807874?s=1743208324&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F393883453958717%2Fposts%2F3468724909807874%3Fs%3D1743208324%26sfns%3Dmo&d=GlETU%2Fuc5qoZzc1QHf9C2iUaeeTarj8%2BpjPG%2B7PQGFg%3D&h=027847cd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/393883453958717/posts/3468724909807874?s=1743208324&amp;sfns=mo</a>"},{"pid":"63adcbd11b682bee3c31c792533411e74bb79a66","tid":1464054,"uid":60545,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:22:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"410244aa5d97a43191cf93796ad036002418fb33","tid":1464054,"uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:22:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3eeb5cc763cd50dbe555b2b23753ba9b936e18c","tid":1464054,"uid":68471,"like":36,"dislike":8,"score":28,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:22:40.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">塞旅客一定要塞如果唔係出機場做咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n塞嘅話，留返一個counter/閘口出黎，放一條極細既路出黎，由佢地排條好長既隊，排都排一兩粒鐘。其他路block Q曬，咁你就人道了，無位比人入了。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n圍師必缺，你唔使塞死，已經塞死。</span>"},{"pid":"f197eb3b97e1f9e1f5f8ac4fb29f2024b1105365","tid":1464054,"uid":36995,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08