好易幫港共加子彈, 畀政府做你一鑊<br />\n當然你又可以話, 你呼吸都畀佢屈, 但你係離境大堂附近聚集, 佢要入你都易好多<br />\n但永遠, 每次D人都唔L聽, 即使宜家都係有人好硬頸<br />\n爬山就大L晒, 咩意見都唔聽<br />\n<br />\n講多次, 入機場, 可做<br />\n但要去ARRIVAL HALL!!<br />\n離境大堂盡量唔好接近!!</span></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">邊個帶頭塞離境大堂, 邊個就有機會係鬼, 馬上檢查佢</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"e15d62c296932989bdb5d8d330d71f85ff2231d8","tid":1464054,"uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:28:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db94dd1e22bba5479fadaad74a09f09db28a6d80","tid":1464054,"uid":64103,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b1e81ec933b5fecc2ad8a6b0d53b33a1dd3b0ddc","tid":1464054,"uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:20:08.000Z","msg":"【學苑即時】居港逾廿年的荷蘭籍女士Irma表示理解示威者在機場的行動，她贊同集會有效，令其在歐洲的親友也因此詢問香港的現況。她續指堵塞離境大堂雖非合適的地方，但仍然支持示威者爭取民主的決心。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/393883453958717/posts/3468724909807874?s=1743208324&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F393883453958717%2Fposts%2F3468724909807874%3Fs%3D1743208324%26sfns%3Dmo&d=GlETU%2Fuc5qoZzc1QHf9C2iUaeeTarj8%2BpjPG%2B7PQGFg%3D&h=027847cd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/393883453958717/posts/3468724909807874?s=1743208324&amp;sfns=mo</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:29:04.000Z","msg":"因為佢係居港廿年<br />\n其他唔了解香港新聞的可能印象就好差"},{"pid":"b1fdfe07432dc2a1fd93b0634a066db65e3dbd47","tid":1464054,"uid":50414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:29:16.000Z","msg":"多謝Irma 小姐"},{"pid":"d74a4e04d325df007e691a2cdb40706f7c622702","tid":1464054,"uid":1315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:29:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f76ccdb9b7e946b600891faea515f4c3a59d2bd1","tid":1464054,"uid":22360,"like